{{Infobox person | name = Vladimir Aleksandrovich Trefilov | image = | caption = | native_name = Владимир Александрович Трефилов | native_name_lang = ru | birth_name = | birth_date = {{Birth date and age|1949|1|16}} | birth_place = [[Izhevsk]], [[Udmurt Autonomous Soviet Socialist Republic]], [[USSR]] | death_date = | death_place = | monuments = | residence = | nationality = Russian | known_for = | television = | education = [[Udmurt State University]] ([[Candidate of Sciences]]) | employer = | notable_works = ''Fundamentals of Religious Studies'' (in co-authorship) | occupation = Scholar, poet, painter, yogi }} '''Vladimir Aleksandrovich Trefilov''' ({{lang-ru|Влади́мир Алекса́ндрович Трефи́лов}}; born 1949) is a [[Russians|Russian]] [[scholar]] of [[religious studies]], [[philosophy of medicine]], author and lecturer. He is also known as a [[poet]], [[painter]] and [[yogi]].
==Biography== Born in [[Izhevsk]], [[Udmurt Autonomous Soviet Socialist Republic]], Trefilov studied [[History]] at [[Udmurt State University]] and [[Philosophy]] at [[Moscow State University]]. From 1975 he works for Izhevsk State Medical Academy. He obtained his [[Candidate of Sciences]] diploma and became in 1991 Head of the Department of Philosophy and Humanities at the Izhevsk State Medical Academy. He is author of over 50 scientific works.{{sfn|ISMA|loc=Трефилов}} In 1992 he studied in United States.{{sfn|Хазова|2001}}
Trefilov is a member of the Academic Council of the [[Mikhail Kalashnikov|Kalashnikov]] Museum,{{sfn|ISMA|loc=Трефилов}} in this museum he reads a cycle of public lectures ''Geopolitics and Military History''.{{sfn|Kalashnikov Museum|loc=Трефилов}}
Trefilov is author a book of sonnets ''Fireseed.'' (1989). In 2001 he became the head of "Udmurt Literature Union". Trefilov's pictures (in genre of "transrealism"{{sfn|Blagorazumov|2012}}) have been displayed at 18 art exhibitions in Russia and there are in many private collections of Russia, England, USA.{{sfn|ISMA|loc=Трефилов}} He has [[Integral yoga|yoga]] teacher's international certificate.{{sfn|Саввиных|2011}}
===Prophecy was fulfilled=== {{external media |float = |width = |topic = Vladimir Trefilov's Prophecy |image1 = [http://farm3.static.flickr.com/2117/1856740191_e60d55108a.jpg?v=0 ''Angel of the Bottomless Pit,'' 1996]{{efn|[[Oil painting|Oil on canvas]], 87 × 132 sm.}}{{efn|"They had as king over them the angel of [[Bottomless pit (Bible)|the Abyss]]..." ([[Book of Revelation|Revelation]] 9:11).}} |image2 = [http://farm3.static.flickr.com/2286/1856763715_b768a93487.jpg?v=0 ''The Star Wormwood,'' 1997]{{efn|Oil on canvas, 92 × 132 sm.}}{{efn|"The name of the star is Wormwood." (Revelation 8:11).}} }} [[File:WTC smoking on 9-11.jpeg|thumb|260px|[[September 11 attacks]]]] Trefilov says he studied in 1992 in USA. Someway, in the beginning of December, surveying during walk on a vicinity of Manhattan, he gazed at "[[World Trade Center (1973–2001)|two enormous buildings]]" and suddenly has thought of fragility of these demonstrative displays of technical progress and is unexpected for itself has presented, as they flare and fall... He says, that, probably, behind it there was a sensation of alarm concerning vulnerability of a civilization, life, a universe. It considers, that, probably, the intuition has worked.{{efn|Trefilof wrote in ''Fundamentals of Religious Studies'', "[[Yogi|High developed man]] in time of dream, [[meditation]], and [[trance]] may leave his body and to work in unphysical worlds. Here no space and temporal barriers exist."{{sfn|Трефилов|2005}}}}{{efn|[[Sarvepalli Radhakrishnan]] wrote, "Transmission of thought from one individual to another without the intervention of the normal communicating mechanisms is quite possible. Through concentration on the threefold modifications which all objects constantly undergo, we acquire the power to know the past, present and the future."{{sfn|Radhakrishnan |2010|p=366}}}} He has returned to "native Izhevsk and has drawn four variants of it, as now began repeat often, apocalypse." Trefilov has finished the first picture in 1996, named its ''Angel of the Bottomless Pit.'' In 1997 there was the second, under the name ''The Star Wormwood.''{{sfn|Хазова|2001}} September 14, 2001 newspaper ''День'' wrote that "on September 12th, 2001 Vladimir Trefilov has urgently organized display of the pictures, considering that they most precisely correspond to the today's validity."{{sfn|День|2001}} After the [[September 11 attacks|terrorist attacks of 11 September]] the fact of Trefilov's prediction evoked a wide public response and was reported both in the press and on TV.<ref>See [https://app.box.com/s/4w3moagrychjv6j43su3 Newspapers about Trefilov's prophecy]</ref>
